// Given an array of daily temperatures, for each day find
// the number of days until a warmer temperature.
// If no future day is warmer, output 0.
// Constraints: n <= 1e5, temp in [30, 100]
// Example: temps = [73,74,75,71,69,72,76,73]
// Output:           [1,  1,  4,  2,  1,  1,  0,  0]

